{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Arlington\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":7,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/pooch-pals-llc-dog-walker\",\"name\":\"Pooch Pals LLC - Dog Walker\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/pooch-pals-llc-dog-walker\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about Pooch Pals LLC - Dog Walker.  What makes this dog facility special is its professional, reliable, excellent. The staff's dedication to creating a positive...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Arlington\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":8,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/glencarlyn-dog-park\",\"name\":\"Glencarlyn Dog Park\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/glencarlyn-dog-park\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about Glencarlyn Dog Park.  What makes this dog facility special is its great, safe. great place for my dog Located in a safe area, This facility specializes in Pet care...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Arlington\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":9,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/glencarlyn-park\",\"name\":\"Glencarlyn Park\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/glencarlyn-park\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about Glencarlyn Park.  What makes this dog facility special is its spacious, professional, reliable. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Arlington\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":10,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/the-royal-pet-resort-and-spa\",\"name\":\"The Royal Pet Resort and Spa\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/the-royal-pet-resort-and-spa\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about The Royal Pet Resort and Spa.  What makes this dog facility special is its professional, reliable, clean. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Arlington\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How much does a dog license cost in Arlington, VA?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Arlington County offers a unique lifetime dog license for a one-time fee of $30. This license remains valid for the life of the dog as long as the rabies vaccination is kept current, making it very pet-owner friendly compared to annual renewals.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are there indoor dog parks in Arlington?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes—Arlington is home to Snouts & Stouts, a massive 12,000+ sq ft indoor dog park and bar. It provides K9 grass, climate control, and supervised play so your dog can socialize while you enjoy a local brew.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Which Arlington dog parks have water access?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Shirlington Dog Park and Glencarlyn Park both offer unique stream access. Shirlington features a fenced-in entry to Four Mile Run, allowing dogs to swim and splash safely in a natural environment.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I take my dog to watch planes at Gravelly Point?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Absolutely. Leashed dogs are welcome at Gravelly Point Park along the Mount Vernon Trail. It’s a famous spot for watching planes land at Reagan National Airport, though it can be very loud for noise-sensitive pets.\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Dog Parks Directory\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Arlington\"}]}</script><header class=\"header header-visible  header-light\"><div class=\"header-container\"><div class=\"header-left\"><a class=\"logo\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"Indoor Dog Park logo\" width=\"140\" height=\"40\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent;object-fit:contain;height:auto\" src=\"/images/logo/logo.png\"/></a></div><div class=\"header-center\"><nav class=\"header-nav\" aria-label=\"Main navigation\"><a class=\"header-nav-link\" href=\"/\">Browse Parks</a><div class=\"header-nav-item\"><button class=\"header-nav-link\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Discover <i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down dropdown-icon \"></i></button><div class=\"header-dropdown \"><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/parks-with-bars\">Parks with Bars</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/training-facilities\">Training Facilities</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/how-it-works\">How It Works</a></div></div><div class=\"header-nav-item\"><button class=\"header-nav-link\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Locations <i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down dropdown-icon \"></i></button><div class=\"header-dropdown \"><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/san-francisco\">San Francisco</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/los-angeles\">Los Angeles</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/san-diego\">San Diego</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/new-york\">New York</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/seattle\">Seattle</a></div></div><a class=\"header-nav-link\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"header-nav-link\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></nav></div><div class=\"header-right\"><a class=\"header-link\" href=\"/contact\">Contact us</a><a class=\"header-link header-link-primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">List your park</a><a class=\"header-link\" href=\"/signup\">Sign up</a><a class=\"header-link\" href=\"/login\">Log in</a><button class=\"menu-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><i class=\"bi bi-list\"></i></button></div></div><div class=\"mobile-menu \" aria-hidden=\"true\"><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/\">Browse Parks</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/parks-with-bars\">Parks with Bars</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/training-facilities\">Training Facilities</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/how-it-works\">How It Works</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/blog\">Blog &amp; Guides</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/contact\">Contact us</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/list-your-park\">List your park</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/signup\">Sign up</a><a class=\"mobile-menu-item\" href=\"/login\">Log in</a></div></header><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 table-of-contents \"><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-progress-bar\"><div style=\"width:0%\" class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-progress-fill\"></div></div><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-container\"><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-header\"><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-title\">Table of Contents</div><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-subtitle\">Jump to any section</span></div><nav class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-nav\"><ul class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-list\"><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">