on class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">10</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Full Directory</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">11</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">Owner &amp; Franchise</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">12</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">FAQs</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">13</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">More Resources</span></button></li></ul></nav><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-actions\"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn toc-action-top\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-up\"></i>Back to Top</button><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-down\"></i>To Bottom</button></div></div></div><main class=\"city-page-layout\"><div class=\"mobile-toc-button\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"mobile-toc-trigger\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-ul\"></i><span>Contents</span></button></div><section id=\"city-hero\" class=\"city-hero-section \"><div class=\"section-shell city-hero-shell\"><div class=\"city-hero-copy\"><div class=\"hero-breadcrumbs\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><span>Dog Parks Directory</span><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><strong>Arlington</strong></div><p class=\"hero-eyebrow\">City spotlight</p><h1>Dog Parks in Arlington, VA</h1><p class=\"hero-description\">Experience the premier pet culture of Arlington, from the historic stream-access runs of Shirlington to the year-round indoor play at Snouts &amp; Stouts.</p><div class=\"city-rich-description\"><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">Arlington, Virginia, stands as a premier destination for urban dog owners, offering a sophisticated infrastructure that balances high-density living with expansive, world-class pet amenities. The county is anchored by the historic <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://parks.arlingtonva.us/locations/shirlington-dog-park/\">Shirlington Dog Park</a>, which was the first off-leash facility in the D.C. area and remains a crown jewel for its unique fenced-in access to Four Mile Run, allowing pups a safe natural swim. For those seeking climate-controlled socialization, <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.snoutsandstouts.com/\">Snouts &amp; Stouts</a> provides a massive 12,000-square-foot indoor park and bar, featuring professional K9 grass and a &quot;beer and treats&quot; concept that caters to the local community year-round. This commitment to canine inclusion is further reflected in the county’s pet-friendly administrative policies, such as the unique $30 lifetime dog license, which eliminates the hassle of annual renewals for residents who keep their rabies vaccinations current.</p><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">Beyond the urban runs, Arlington offers iconic outdoor experiences along the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.nps.gov/gwmp/planyourvisit/mtvernon-trail.htm\">Mount Vernon Trail</a>, where leashed dogs can accompany their owners to highlights like Gravelly Point Park to experience the roar of planes descending into Reagan National Airport. Local favorite <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://lostdogcafe.com/\">Lost Dog Cafe</a> in Westover further enriches the culture, as its success supports a rescue foundation that has saved tens of thousands of animals, making dining out a philanthropic tradition for local dog lovers. For those exploring the market for new pet facilities, our <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/owner-resources\">owner resources</a> detail the high demand and zoning nuances found in vibrant districts like Clarendon and Rosslyn. Whether splashing in the stream at <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://parks.arlingtonva.us/locations/glencarlyn-park-dog-park/\">Glencarlyn Park</a> or relaxing on a brewery patio, Arlington provides a world-class environment where pets are truly integrated into every facet of civic life.</p></div><div class=\"hero-cta-row\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta primary\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-check\"></i>Browse directory</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta ghost\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i>Open map</button><a class=\"hero-cta text-link\" href=\"/list-your-park\"><i class=\"bi bi-plus-circle\"></i>Submit a park</a></div><div class=\"hero-footnotes\"><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Data refreshed weekly</span><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Live availability coming soon</span></div></div><div class=\"city-hero-visual\"><div class=\"hero-image-card\"><img alt=\"Arlington dog park landscape\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/cities/arlington-va/hero.webp\"/><div class=\"hero-image-gradient\"></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"city-premium-section\" aria-labelledby=\"city-premium-heading\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"city-premium-header\"><div><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Premium spotlight</span><h2 id=\"city-premium-heading\">Premium parks in <!-- -->Arlington</h2><p>Partners highlighted here are currently investing in featured placement across this guide.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-header-actions\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">Feature my park</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to sales</a></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-values\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-megaphone\"></i></div><h4>Pinned above free listings</h4><p>Premium partners appear before every other card within the city directory.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-envelope-paper\"></i></div><h4>Lead-friendly CTAs</h4><p>Direct website + phone buttons encourage bookings straight from this page.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h4>Always-on exposure</h4><p>Featured cards show even when we haven’t processed new static data yet.</p></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-grid\"><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"city-insights\" class=\"city-insights-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><section id=\"city-statistics\" class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db city-stats-unified\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-section-header\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-eyebrow\">City Statistics</span><h2 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">How <!-- -->Arlington<!-- --> stacks up for dog families</h2><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-intro\">Verified ratings, review volume, and park availability updated directly from our community directory.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stats-row\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card accent\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Smart Policy</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">Lifetime $30 License</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Arlington simplifies ownership with a one-time lifetime license fee, ensuring long-term health compliance without the stress of annual renewals.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Unique Access</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">Stream-Side Splashing</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Multiple local parks like Shirlington and Glencarlyn feature rare, fenced-in natural stream access, perfect for aquatic socialization in a safe setting.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Year-Round Play</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">Snouts &amp; Stouts Indoor</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">A massive 12,000+ sq ft indoor facility offers a climate-controlled sanctuary with a bar, making it the ultimate social hub for Arlington pups.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-row\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-header\"><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">Most common amenities</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">What people are looking for and finding in <!-- -->Arlington<!-- -->.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-chips\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Onsite services</span></span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Indoor facilities</span></span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Professional staff</span></span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Climate controlled</span></span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Parking available</span></span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Easy access</span></span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db data-grid-container\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db key-metrics-grid\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item primary\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-geo-alt-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-details\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-number\">39</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-label\">Total Dog Parks</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-sub\">All types combined</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-star-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-details\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-number\">4.6</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-label\">Average Rating</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-sub\">Based on <!-- -->8,913<!-- --> reviews</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-chat-heart-fill\"></i></div><div class