t For</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-list\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Casual outings</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Dining with pets</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Shopping trips</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Social experiences</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">What to Bring</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-list\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Leash</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Portable water bowl</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Calm temperament</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Training treats</span></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Pro Tips</h4><ul class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d tips-list\"><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Call ahead to confirm pet policy</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Keep your dog leashed at all times</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Ensure your dog is well-behaved in public</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Respect other customers</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Be prepared to leave if your dog becomes anxious</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-footer\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d expand-toggle\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">View guide</span><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></button><a class=\"jump-link\" href=\"#dog-friendly-establishment-parks\">Jump to list<i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-arrow-right\"></i></a></div></article></div></section></div><div id=\"neighborhood-clusters\" style=\"margin-top:80px;padding-top:80px;border-top:1px solid #f1f5f9\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Local Districts</span><h2>Where to play in <!-- -->Arlington</h2><p>Semantic clusters of dog-friendly highlights broken down by neighborhood.</p></div><div class=\"collection-grid\" style=\"margin-top:40px\"><article class=\"collection-card\" style=\"border:1px solid #f1f5f9;background:#f8fafc\"><div class=\"collection-card-head\"><span class=\"collection-pill\">0<!-- --> spots found</span><h3>Shirlington</h3></div><p>Home to the county’s most famous dog park and many pet-friendly patios.</p><div class=\"collection-card-footer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta text-link\">Browse directory<i class=\"bi bi-arrow-right\"></i></button></div></article><article class=\"collection-card\" style=\"border:1px solid #f1f5f9;background:#f8fafc\"><div class=\"collection-card-head\"><span class=\"collection-pill\">0<!-- --> spots found</span><h3>Clarendon/Rosslyn</h3></div><p>High-energy urban hubs with modern indoor facilities and rooftop dog runs.</p><div class=\"collection-card-footer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta text-link\">Browse directory<i class=\"bi bi-arrow-right\"></i></button></div></article><article class=\"collection-card\" style=\"border:1px solid #f1f5f9;background:#f8fafc\"><div class=\"collection-card-head\"><span class=\"collection-pill\">0<!-- --> spots found</span><h3>Westover</h3></div><p>Charming neighborhood anchored by the iconic and philanthropic Lost Dog Cafe.</p><div class=\"collection-card-footer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta text-link\">Browse directory<i class=\"bi bi-arrow-right\"></i></button></div></article></div></div></div></section><section id=\"map-and-neighborhoods\" class=\"map-experience-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Interactive planning</span><h2>See everything laid out on the map</h2><p>Use the live map to lock in nearby options, preview ratings, and save time hopping between neighborhoods.</p></div><div class=\"map-grid\"><div class=\"map-panel\"><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><div style=\"min-height:320px;background:#f3f4f6\"></div><!--/$--></div><div class=\"map-sidebar\"><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Quick filters</h3><div class=\"map-chip-grid\"><button type=\"button\"><span>Dog Park</span><small>38</small></button><button type=\"button\"><span>Dog-Friendly Establishment</span><small>1</small></button></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Highest-rated nearby</h3><div class=\"mini-park-list\"><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Arlington Dog Daycare and Boarding</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>5.0</strong></div><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Bark Park</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>5.0</strong></div><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Club Canine Cardio</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>5.0</strong></div></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card muted\"><p>Tip: tap any map marker to open directions, amenities, and current open hours.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"planning-essentials\" class=\"planning-essentials-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Visit toolkit</span><h2>Plan the perfect dog outing in <!-- -->Arlington</h2><p>Borrow best practices from local trainers, rangers, and experienced pet parents.</p></div><div class=\"planning-grid\"><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-patch-check\"></i></div><h3>Legal Essentials</h3><ul><li>Secure a lifetime license for a one-time $30 fee</li><li>Must keep rabies vaccinations current for validity</li><li>Dog tags must be worn at all times in public</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i></div><h3>Top Social Spots</h3><ul><li>Shirlington Dog Park (Quarter-mile long run)</li><li>Gravelly Point (Plane watching with leashed pups)</li><li>New District Brewing (Dog-friendly local taps)</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-shield-check\"></i></div><h3>Safety &amp; Etiquette</h3><ul><li>Avoid Gravelly Point for noise-sensitive dogs</li><li>Vaccination records required for indoor parks</li><li>Strict leash laws in all non-fenced public areas</li></ul></article></div></div></section><section id=\"expert-tips\" class=\"expert-tips-section\" style=\"padding:80px 0\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div style=\"padding:48px;background:#f8fafc;border-radius:24px;border:1px solid #e2e8f0\"><div style=\"display:flex;gap:24px;align-items:flex-start;flex-wrap:wrap\"><div style=\"width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:16px;background:#6366f1;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-size:1.5rem;flex-shrink:0\"><i class=\"bi bi-lightbulb\"></i></div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:300px\"><span style=\"font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;color:#6366f1;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em\">Expert Advice</span><h2 style=\"font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin-top:8px\">Internal Tips for <!-- -->Arlington<!-- --> Dog Owners</h2><p style=\"color:#64748b;margin-top:12px;line-height:1.6\">Our team and local community members shared these specific insights to help you navigate <!-- -->Arlington<!-- --> like a pro.</p><ul style=\"margin-top:32px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));gap:24px;list-style:none;padding:0\"><li style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start\"><i class=\"bi bi-check2-circle\" style=\"color:#10b981;font-size:1.25rem;margin-top:2px\"></i><span style=\"color:#334155;fon